    <title>Employee ownership, next steps: government response to the Nuttall review</title>
    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary></summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Sets out the Government’s response to each of the 28 recommendations made in the Nuttall review of employee ownership (URN 12/933). Focuses on existing companies that are already employee-owned or are thinking about taking that step, as well as those starting up for whom employee ownership might be a good business model to adopt. See also the consultation 12/1162 for the consultation on employee ownership and share buy backs, and 12/1215 for the consultation on implementing employee owner status.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
