    <category>Publication</category>
    <summary></summary>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Respond by 16 November 2012. Consultation seeking views on company law provisions around share buy backs. Focuses on improving the operation of internal share markets to support companies using direct share ownership, including holding private company shares in treasury and facilitating share buy backs. See also URN 12/933 for the Nuttall review of employee ownership, 12/1161 for the government response, 12/1165 for an impact assessment and 12/1248 for related draft regulations.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
